metadata.name: Christmas.eth
metadata.description: I always wanted my first NFT on Foundation to mean something, so I created Christmas ETH. The perfect gift for the web3 Love. Celebrating our first ETH Christmas after so many successful projects. Tons of NFTs and marketplaces were launched. Some failed, some were successful. I'm glad Foundation stayed! Merry Christmas.eth everyone. More rare's to your collection! & Happy Christmas.eth to Foundation.
